<div style="background-color: #7700015C; border-left: 12px solid #D92121; padding: 2.5px 16.8px; margin: 0.5em 0em; font-size:36px; font-family:Orator STD;">Entrances and Exits</div>
===<span style="font-family:Orator STD;">Entrances</span>===
*Opening a supply crate in [[Level 1]] containing molten metal might lead one here. 
*Entering an out-of-place black door in [[Level 221]] leads wanderers here.
===<span style="font-family:Orator STD;">Exits</span>===
*A series of hallways hidden in a secret chamber labelled ''"Project TCCS"''  will take one to [[Level 443]]. 
*Staring at a skylight for 4 minutes leads one to [[Level 200]].
*Entering a brown door leads one to [[Level 998]].
*Noclipping through a surface shone by sunlight sends one to [[Level 500]].
*A Japanese-styled door sends one to [[Level 51]].
*Noclipping through a furnace sends one to [[The Delta Mall]].

